Introduction

THE T-BIRD was a five-member project boy band managed by OD Entertainment. They made their debut on March 19, 2019, with the single “Rock Star.”

Unfortunately, the group disbanded in late 2019 due to inactivity on their social media platforms. Notably, they were described as a “popsical” group, blending elements of K-pop with musical influences.
